Here’s an example of one of my existing modules

```{% set href = module.cta_link.url.href %}
{% if module.cta_link.url.type is equalto "EMAIL_ADDRESS" %}
{% set href = "mailto:" + href %}
{% endif %}
&lt;section class="section module-footer-cta"&gt;
  &lt;div class="container"&gt;
    &lt;div class="columns is-centered"&gt;
      &lt;div class="column is-10 is-paddingless"&gt;
        &lt;div class="content has-text-centered"&gt;
          &lt;h2&gt;
            {{ module.cta_text }}
          &lt;/h2&gt;
          &lt;a href="{{ href }}" class="button is-primary is-large"
            {% if module.cta_link.open_in_new_tab %}target="_blank" {% endif %}
            {% if module.cta_link.no_follow %}rel="nofollow" {% endif %}&gt;
            {{ module.button_text }}
          &lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;```

